qcom-agm (2.0.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Introduced new APIs for SPR shared memory allocation and deallocation.
  * Added support for retrieving available frame count using GSL.
  * Added hs0 interface support and period_size setting in agmplay.
  * Introduced get_timestamp API for tinyalsa test.
  * Updated Debian package control file metadata.
  * Improved internal plugin handling and session timing.

